==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Heliconia
<hw>Hel`i*co"ni*a</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL. See
<er>Helicon</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>One of numerous species
of <gen>Heliconius</gen>, a genus of tropical American butterflies. The
wings are usually black, marked with green, crimson, and
white.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

